---
title: Chicken Nuggies & Cheesy Mash Mountain with Broccoli Forest & Gravy
description: It’s all hands on deck, this recipe is designed to be cooked by grown-ups and kids together! This meal is so fun, even the adults will want to play with their food. Don’t worry, it’s not just here for show - those golden chicken nuggets are too tasty to resist. And don’t forget the cheesy potato mountain! That river of gravy running through it is calling your name.
